  <comment localId="7" height="24" width="114">
    <position x="206" y="4" />
    <content>
      <html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
        <head>
          <title />
        </head>
        <body>
          <p style="color:#ff00ff;font-family:Calibri;font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-size:14pt;">Settings of the SD1207 card:&lt;br /&gt;  FUNCTION MODE: Mode A-A&lt;br /&gt;  UNIT: Increments / min&lt;br /&gt;  TIME BASE: 2000ms (Speed is averaged in a time window of 2s)</p>
        </body>
      </html>
    </content>
  </comment>
